name: DBEntriesReport
tagline: Python 3.3 script which populates mySQL database and analyzes entries
body:
Python script which populates MySQL database with a large number of email addresses, tracks number of emails registered on a particular domain, and produces a monthly report of top-5 email domains sorted by growth. Script is scalable with regards to a number of emails/domains. Done as a test task for an interview over the course of a few days.
